rComments: Definitely best prof for this class. He is so nice and his exams were super easy - no surprises and he grades generously. He dropped our worst midterm grade too which boosted the class average by a lot. DGDs were very very helpful they helped me get a good final grade because the TA covered everything that we needed to know. Overall AMAZING class.

If Jake Peralta from Brookyn 99 had a PhD and adored organic electronic devices, it would be Prof. Lessard. Very fun professor who also knew the material well. Multiple tests gave opportunity to succeed. 10/10 would recommend his class.
Very good professor! Entertaining and tells you exactly what you need to know for exams. Assignments are very indicative of exams and makes a relatively dry course bearable!
He is a very goid professor. Tells you exactly what you need to know and what is expected on the exam. The midterm was an easy 100% class average was 87%!!

Nouveau prof, et c'est claire qu'il ne sait pas les materiaux du cours, car il n'est pas capable de repondre aux questions des etudiants. Il n'etait jamais disponible a son bureau. Des fois, il a rigole aux questions des etudiants en class.
